<TEXT>
   Irish Foriegn Minister Brian Lenihan, who
has a serious blood disorder, left Wednesday to undergo treatment
at the renowned Mayo Clinic in Rochester, Minn.
   Lenihan, 58, who is also the deputy prime minister, flew from
